6 năm trước. Đây là nhân vật then chốt để tìm kiếm ra manh mối sự việc. Kim Seol Hyun đóng vai nữ cảnh sát xinh đẹp có thiên phú, miệt mài truy tìm, là người gánh việc đánh nhau, uống rượu trong đội. Lee Chung Ah đóng vai điều tra viên của FBI. Yoon Sun Woo đóng vai kỹ sư thần bí chấp hành nhiệm vụ bí mật.</p>","tmdb_id":113113,"cast":["Namkoong Min","Kim Seol-hyun","Lee Chung-ah","Yoon Sun-woo","Kim Chang-wan","Shin Jae-whi","Kim Won-hae","Lee Sin-young","Jung Dae-ro","An Si-ha","Bae Hyun-kyung","Baek Ji-won","Yoon Kyung-ho","Kim Ki-nam","Choi Dae-chul"],"director":["Jeong-hyeon Kim"],"keywords":[],"tmdb":{"type":"tv","id":"113113","season":1,"vote_average":7.956,"vote_count":34},"cast_meta":[{"name":"Namkoong Min","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Namkoong Min","tmdb_id":1239247,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/aQ6AzP9dEyhml9bhQCr0vvEGkrk.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1239247"},{"name":"Kim Seol-hyun","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Kim Seol-hyun","tmdb_id":1374514,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/Ac9fQziYllkpwGURJwqfadUnokn.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1374514"},{"name":"Lee Chung-ah","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Lee Chung-ah","tmdb_id":126743,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/jCF77VweJYzkmilO0E7SFPFGbT7.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/126743"},{"name":"Yoon Sun-woo","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Yoon Sun-woo","tmdb_id":1616369,"profile":null,"tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1616369"},{"name":"Kim Chang-wan","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Kim Chang-wan","tmdb_id":63441,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/g1F7rIJ1FVMct4O0Q6B63RD7ICd.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/63441"},{"name":"Shin Jae-whi","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Shin Jae-whi","tmdb_id":2805080,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/s4od0kMYFzJkJN5cU0HKlBmGkU2.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/2805080"},{"name":"Kim Won-hae","name_vi":null,"name_ori